<br>
I just wanna strewss that getting in there isn't like walking in through the fear portal. Ok here's a better example. With a full raiding party (Valoran) it took us around 5 hours to get to that point and thats clearing everything as we moved. The other way to get there is to have a cleric, mage and monk do the run in and hope they live to get there. without knowing the pathing of the creatures.. it is near impossible. <br>
<br>
Before you try, please PLEASE look into it ALOT and make sure you have a necro for corpse pulling and a friendly cleric nearby to rez. You will probably need them =(<br>
<br>
Your other option is to ask a bigger guild if you can get a Call down. Some might say yes, some might say no. I dont know.<br>
<br>
PS. dont forget a porter to get out <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
To get items in there you need to collect cards, they come in 4 colors and 4 types example red throne, blue crown.<br>
<br>
Different items need different combos of cards to combine in the container. All the good items require at least 1 throne card, which since they nerfed the drop rate are like a 1 in 1000 kills to get one.  It might not even be the right color, you need for the combination you want. So it's not &quot;drops&quot; as you and I know it, its all combine container stuff like quests.<br>
<br>
Ravenlark &amp; Vree<br>
